    {
      "id": "PopularPost322787",
      "post_content": "You know, I don't think this guy is as bad as people say. I mean yeah, he's not exactly good and [Mindless Automaton](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindless Automaton) is far better, but he's in a fairly supported creature type now (due to the Splicers from New Phyrexia) and he has does get counters for {1} and a discard, which can be a possibly good thing.  \n   \nMake no mistake, he's not by any means good, but I do think he deserves a 1.5-2 instead of a 1 or lower.",
      "posted_by": "NARFNra",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost322787\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">You know, I don't think this guy is as bad as people say. I mean yeah, he's not exactly good and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mindless Automaton\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindless Automaton\">Mindless Automaton</a> is far better, but he's in a fairly supported creature type now (due to the Splicers from New Phyrexia) and he has does get counters for {1} and a discard, which can be a possibly good thing.<br/> <br/>Make no mistake, he's not by any means good, but I do think he deserves a 1.5-2 instead of a 1 or lower.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '322787'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy48472\">NARFNra</span>\r\n                                (6/17/2013 10:30:12 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src